subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which emperor established the city of Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर के नए निवास करने वाले मुख्यालय कौन सा था?
explanation_en: Sawai Jai Singh is the emperor who established Jaipur. He built the city in 1727 under the name 'Pink City' due to the color of the walls built by him.
